               <p>
                  <rs id="t17840421-32-verdict188" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840421-32-verdict188" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840421-32-verdict188" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               GUILTY Of stealing, but not in the dwelling house
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>To be each <rs id="t17840421-32-punish189" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840421-32-punish189" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840421-32-defend538 t17840421-32-punish189"></join>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840421-32-defend540 t17840421-32-punish189"></join>
               transported seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Baron EYRE.</p>
